          "reviewBody": "They even not taking proper interview's for children last year we were going through financially crisis my elder daughter was in sindhi model itself we paid donation 50000/- I have receipt & it was refundable when we took a t.c we did not get our refundable amount.\nLast year we tried again for sindhi model for my elder & younger daughter they has seats but they did not gave admission actually they only looks for big donation & rich people's. I should go to court for donation which is elegal but I don't want to make my time waste trustees of this school have big contacts..",
