            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "As an alumna of SMS, I had a wonderful experience, and I love and miss school. Up until the passing of my batch in the least, there was a good quality of education, especially in the higher levels of education (i.e. high school), with experienced staff members and priority to conceptual understanding and comprehension duly present. I truly enjoyed childhood here, and made some wonderful friends, and I'm truly grateful to my school for sculpting me into the person I am today.",
